name: Fortraits 1 - Yorgie
description:
Forts and Portraits. Fortraits. The first of a series. 

Fortraits 1

Yorgie knows what it is to be without a home. He’s seen some rough times. Gone are his days and nights of scrubbing the greasy vents in the tannery behind the gas station. After which he’d creep off to his corner in the damp alley, for another fitful night's sleep under the tarp. Listening to the rain. Having ultimately prevailed when many around him thought for sure he was done, he’s in a much better place. The fact that his new fortress is a bit cramped doesn’t bother him in the slightest. Perfection is rare and fleeting. The realms of gratitude and compassion - that’s where the magic is. And that’s where our man now resides. He feels alive for the first time.
